            <div className="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
                <SectionHead
                    eyebrow="What's in the box"
                    title="A real framework, not a toy."
                    sub="One file is the headline. Underneath is a full-stack runtime — routing, SSR, a dev server, and the seams you actually ship on."
                />

                <div className="grid gap-3 sm:gap-4 lg:grid-cols-6">
                    {/* Routing — wide, with a mini route map */}
                    <BentoCell className="lg:col-span-3" icon="M3.75 9.776c.112-.017.227-.026.344-.026h15.812c.117 0 .232.009.344.026M4.5 9.75V6A2.25 2.25 0 016.75 3.75h3.879a1.5 1.5 0 011.06.44l2.122 2.12a1.5 1.5 0 001.06.44h4.629A2.25 2.25 0 0121.75 9v.75" title="File-based routing">
                        <p className="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Drop a file in <code className="rounded bg-zinc-100 px-1 text-[0.85em] text-emerald-700 dark:bg-white/10 dark:text-emerald-300">pages/</code> and it's a route. Dynamic segments, catch-alls, nested layouts.</p>
                        <div className="mt-4 space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200/70 bg-zinc-50 p-3 font-mono text-[11.5px] dark:border-white/5 dark:bg-white/[0.03]">
                            {[['pages/index.pyxl', '/'], ['pages/blog/[slug].pyxl', '/blog/:slug'], ['pages/api/health.py', '/api/health']].map(([f, r]) => (
                                <div key={f} className="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
                                    <span className="truncate text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">{f}</span>
                                    <span className="shrink-0 text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400">{r}</span>
                                </div>
                            ))}
                        </div>
                    </BentoCell>

                    {/* SSR — wide, with a flow */}
                    <BentoCell className="lg:col-span-3" delay={80} icon="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 004.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 001.332-7.257 3 3 0 00-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 00-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 002.25 15z" title="SSR, then hydrate">
                        <p className="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Every page renders on the server for instant first paint, then hydrates into a live React app. SEO and speed, for free.</p>
                        <div className="mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px]">
                            {['@server loads', 'HTML streamed', 'React hydrates'].map((s, i) => (
                                <React.Fragment key={s}>
                                    <span className="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2 py-1 text-zinc-600 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:text-zinc-300">{s}</span>
                                    {i < 2 && <span className="text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600">→</span>}
                                </React.Fragment>
                            ))}
                        </div>
                    </BentoCell>

                    {/* Three compact cells */}
                    <BentoCell className="lg:col-span-2" delay={40} icon="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" title="Instant HMR">
                        <p className="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Vite-powered dev server. Edit a <code className="rounded bg-zinc-100 px-1 text-[0.85em] text-emerald-700 dark:bg-white/10 dark:text-emerald-300">.pyxl</code>, see it instantly — hashed assets in prod.</p>
                    </BentoCell>
                    <BentoCell className="lg:col-span-2" delay={120} icon="M14.25 6.087c0-.355.186-.676.401-.959.221-.29.349-.634.349-1.003 0-1.036-1.007-1.875-2.25-1.875s-2.25.84-2.25 1.875c0 .369.128.713.349 1.003.215.283.401.604.401.959v0a.64.64 0 01-.657.643 48.39 48.39 0 01-4.163-.3c.186 1.613.293 3.25.315 4.907a.656.656 0 01-.658.663v0c-.355 0-.676-.186-.959-.401a1.647 1.647 0 00-1.003-.349c-1.036 0-1.875 1.007-1.875 2.25s.84 2.25 1.875 2.25c.369 0 .713-.128 1.003-.349.283-.215.604-.401.959-.401v0c.31 0 .555.26.532.57a48.039 48.039 0 01-.642 5.056c1.518.19 3.058.309 4.616.354a.64.64 0 00.657-.643v0c0-.355-.186-.676-.401-.959a1.647 1.647 0 01-.349-1.003c0-1.035 1.008-1.875 2.25-1.875 1.243 0 2.25.84 2.25 1.875 0 .369-.128.713-.349 1.003-.215.283-.4.604-.4.959v0c0 .333.277.599.61.58a48.1 48.1 0 005.427-.63 48.05 48.05 0 00.582-4.717.532.532 0 00-.533-.57v0c-.355 0-.676.186-.959.401-.29.221-.634.349-1.003.349-1.035 0-1.875-1.007-1.875-2.25s.84-2.25 1.875-2.25c.37 0 .713.128 1.003.349.283.215.604.401.96.401v0a.656.656 0 00.658-.663 48.422 48.422 0 00-.37-5.36c-1.676.05-3.343.196-4.992.435a.643.643 0 01-.74-.633v0z" title="Middleware & plugins">
                        <p className="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">ASGI middleware, an official plugin system, and a CLI you can extend. Auth, DB, and more — opt in.</p>
                    </BentoCell>
                    <BentoCell className="lg:col-span-2" delay={200} icon="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418" title="Deploys anywhere">
                        <p className="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">It's a standard ASGI app under the hood — <code className="rounded bg-zinc-100 px-1 text-[0.85em] text-emerald-700 dark:bg-white/10 dark:text-emerald-300">pyxle build</code>, then run it anywhere Python runs.</p>
                    </BentoCell>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    );
}


